data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3180 sq ft, 5 bedroom 3 bath home has great views of the Mission Mountains out of almost every window!  Feel immediatly comfortable, and welcomed when entering the home with an open concept, cozy fireplace, and kitchen that boasts a double oven, a walk-in pantry, and open to the living room perfect for entertaining! Enjoy having an amazing large master on the main floor that has a beautiful large bathroom! The home includes a lot of storage, two hot water heaters, new flooring, new trim, two hookups for two separate washer/dryers, and an amazing family room or recorational room! Please call Amber Isbell 406-951-0849 or your real estate professional!
